Description: The Israelites leaving Egypt, Moses at right points with his right hand, a female figure carrying an urn is prostrate before him. 1576 Engraving
Curator's comments: This is a first proof impression with the date 1576.The principal figures in this print occur in Polidoro's drawing of 'Moses Striking the Rock' (Pierpont Morgan Library, inv.IV.19. See P. Leone de Castris, Polidoro da Caravaggio. L'opera completa', Naples, 2001, cat. D 177).
